Apart from a positioning bug putting a black bar at the top of the screen on every watch face (and in every launcher tried, I suspect some sort of immersive clash), the user interface isn't responsive enough to rescale on such a small display.    The Watchface designer part is great, and the watches do indeed work and look brilliant on tablets and phones, but for those of us with standard Android watches, forget it... it's not the magic bullet we've been looking for...
